 id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.gomentor.com/articles/shock-trauma\">Gomentor shock trauma</a>, Retrieved 2 April 2018</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://weinholds.org/what-is-developmental-trauma-2/\">Weinholds developmental trauma</a>, retrieved 2 April 2018</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nParsed by mw2238\nCached time: 20180918170219\nCache expiry: 1900800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.136 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.178 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 533/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 0/1500000\nPost\u2010expand include size: 11496/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 589/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 11/40\nExpensive parser function count: 2/500\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post\u2010expand size: 4856/5000000 bytes\nNumber of Wikibase entities loaded: 0/400\nLua time usage: 0.061/10.000 seconds\nLua memory usage: 2.15 MB/50 MB\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  157.395      1 -total\n 39.73%   62.537      1 Template:Reflist\n 38.15%   60.052      1 Template:Medref\n 28.11%   44.238      2 Template:Cite_book\n 23.50%   36.995      1 Template:Ambox\n 13.62%   21.431      1 Template:Request_quotation\n 11.62%   18.284      1 Template:Fix\n  5.28%    8.309      1 Template:Delink\n  4.20%    6.616      1 Template:Category_handler\n  3.08%    4.854      5 Template:Rp\n-->\n\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key enwiki:pcache:idhash:2389884-0!canonical and timestamp 20180918170219 and revision id 843507915\n -->\n</div>"},"langlinks":[{"lang":"da","url":"https://da.wikipedia.org/wiki/Somatic_Experiencing","langname